data.description: This is the one.  A great price point in Greenville with the features that everyone wants.  This newer home (built in 2005) highlights a cathedral ceiling, private backyard that backs up to dense foliage, and a great open floorplan that gives you plenty of living space that lays out on one level.  This is your opportunity to live close to Furman and the Prisma Swamp Rabbit Trail with plenty of local places to eat and shop within a short drive.  This well maintained home has some fresh paint and is move-in ready!
